{"tid":347014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【網上熱話】到底哪個容器會最快盛滿？","createTime":"2017-08-04T12:19:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-05T03:40:32.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"980d1dc205d451ba5eb510a7be80201551650907","tid":347014,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T12:19:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170804/s00001/c1c21b5bddbbf471c2e680afcbf1ebd4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170804%2Fs00001%2Fc1c21b5bddbbf471c2e680afcbf1ebd4.gif&h=210d6f16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日，網上流傳一幅有趣圖片，圖中有12個容器互相接駁在一起，而水龍頭位於右上方的容器上，問若水龍頭開啟後，到底哪一個容器會最快盛滿，引起網民討論。<br />\n<br />\n有一名網友做了一張Gif動圖，展示水龍頭一直開啟時水的流向，並指出最快盛滿的是容器F。<br />\n<br />\n理工大學機械工程學系前工程師盧覺強接受查詢時同意，容器F將會最快盛滿。他解釋，水向低流，位於較高的容器內的水會透過管道流向位置較低的容器。因此，根據圖中情況，水會經過各個容器而流向位置較低且相通的容器F。<br />\n<br />\n部分網民就留言，認為容器G是最快盛滿。他指出，圖中有「陷阱」，仔細看能發現部分連接容器的管道是不相通，影響容器盛滿的次序，又稱當所有管道相通，水經過容器C後會率先流向容器D，然後直接流進容器G，那麼容器G就會是最快盛滿。"},{"pid":"07f52955583d014fd8d79102a2984260c22ca61c","tid":347014,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T12:21:34.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"b3e062f617f148a4499b8225b57bf1a23855a877","tid":347014,"uid":132020,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T12:32:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://s2.quickmeme.com/img/24/240703225e9b031c0ed6d7de595f1dde79283646861394788cd207335e9c209d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs2.quickmeme.com%2Fimg%2F24%2F240703225e9b031c0ed6d7de595f1dde79283646861394788cd207335e9c209d.jpg&h=92d4959f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"61269b3529e9692b15fc694878c7dbdcc80c4c16","tid":347014,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T12:34:52.000Z","msg":"幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e68a408bbcf89b2b642af2b5f422d8134ee41ea3","tid":347014,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T12:35:49.000Z","msg":"馬桶咪裝唔滿囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c543d98d6ab627370ff4dd87f5cd268ade35255b","tid":347014,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T12:49:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b84cc15e0e27452c07e44770c582ee34001a122","tid":347014,"uid":120753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T13:27:56.000Z","msg":"是撚但啦"},{"pid":"db665ea72370b114356c304e610ca3181b1aab56","tid":347014,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T13:32:19.000Z","msg":"關我撚事"},{"pid":"58156132068244e3d1b6ae3702c2af020f0d939c","tid":347014,"uid":36817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T13:42:33.000Z","msg":"F"},{"pid":"5f87cf120b104991b381a28dcd0a61c601eb7a0f","tid":347014,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T13:42:38.000Z","msg":"裝屎定裝乜先"},{"pid":"33dfc0efa6c453c1b91c7d32b3b0a53532348ada","tid":347014,"uid":58358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T13:45:08.000Z","msg":"引網民討論<br />\n咩人先會討論呢啲野"},{"pid":"190dc34ca95f32ada345a8fadcbd5c3ee5e97ed0","tid":347014,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T02:01:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d606f228355609784559db97d64343df2a9f017","tid":347014,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T03:14:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>引網民討論<br />\n咩人先會討論呢啲野</blockquote><br />\n正常人"},{"pid":"896673a51d8d9e235a7d61769ce28ef6001f057f","tid":347014,"uid":128594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T03:40:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>引網民討論<br />\n咩人先會討論呢啲野</blockquote><br />\n有好奇心既人"}]}